text: Ohidur Rahman is a Communist Party of Bangladesh politician and the former Member of Parliament of Naogaon-2. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Naogaon-2 as a Communist Party of Bangladesh candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Communist Party of Bangladesh politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Naogaon District
title: Ohidur Rahman
